	<p>The windsor body micro benchmark is designed to enable weak scaling analysis, through which we can identify remaining bottlenecks in our code and push towards exascale computing. Identifying optimization potential based on industry relevant cases will help us develop innovative technology for efficient simulations in real world design processes. Our team is working tirelessly to create cutting-edge software and we look forward to seeing the positive impact it will have on the industry</p>
